
## DOOR GLASS AND GUIDE REMOVAL/INSTALLATION  


1. Raise the front edge of the door glass 225 mm (8.86 in) from the fully-lowered position.  
2. Disconnect the negative battery cable.  
3. Remove the door screen. (Refer to 09-11 DOOR DISASSEMBLY/ASSEMBLY.)  
4. Remove in the order indicated in the table.  
5. Install in the reverse order of removal.  
6. Adjust the door glass. (Refer to 09-12 DOOR GLASS ADJUSTMENT.)  

